org.jamsim.ascape.stats

Class StatsPredicateRow<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jamsim.ascape.stats.StatsPredicateRow<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - scape member

    public class StatsPredicateRow<T>
extends Object
    A stats row that represents a predicate, a denominator function, and a denominator value. Can be combined with a function to produce a CollectorFunction via a call to getCollectorFunction(StatsFunction, Scape).
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    Oliver Mannion
